maintext:
INDIANAPOLIS (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday evening’s drawing of the Indiana Lottery’s “Quick Draw Evening” game were:
08-11-16-17-33-34-36-37-39-40-41-42-43-56-70-71-74-75-76-79, BE: 40
(eight, eleven, sixteen, seventeen, thirty-three, thirty-four, thirty-six, thirty-seven, thirty-nine, forty, forty-one, forty-two, forty-three, fifty-six, seventy, seventy-one, seventy-four, seventy-five, seventy-six, seventy-nine; BE: forty)
